Various green tints are used to reflect the year in which the latest US Topo products have been published. The service is updated daily and contains the same data used for US Topo footprints in the Map Locator and Downloader application programming interface in the USGS Store - store.usgs.gov.  In addition to access through The National Map Viewer, US Topo products and other USGS publications are available through the USGS Store. For additional information, go to nationalmap.gov.</Abstract>   <KeywordList>    <Keyword/>   </KeywordList>   <OnlineResource xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple"
